    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        A New Derivation of the Propagator&#39;s Path Integral for Spinless Elementary Particles
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Napoletani%2C+D">Domenico Napoletani</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Struppa%2C+D+C">Daniele C. Struppa</a>
      
