        Extracting Bayesian networks from multiple copies of a quantum system
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Micadei%2C+K">Kaonan Micadei</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Landi%2C+G+T">Gabriel T. Landi</a>, 
      
