    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Conjectures on Hidden Onsager Algebra Symmetries in Interacting Quantum Lattice Models
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
