    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Observation of nonlocal quantum interference between the origins of a four-photon state in a silicon chip
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Feng%2C+L">Lan-Tian Feng</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Zhang%2C+M">Ming Zhang</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Liu%2C+D">Di Liu</a>, 
      
