    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        Discrete Solitons of the Ginzburg-Landau Equation
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Salerno%2C+M">Mario Salerno</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Abdullaev%2C+F+K">Fatkhulla Kh. Abdullaev</a>
      
