        Hidden symmetry in the biased Dicke model
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Lu%2C+X">Xilin Lu</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Li%2C+Z">Zi-Min Li</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Mangazeev%2C+V+V">Vladimir V. Mangazeev</a>, 
      
