    <p class="title is-5 mathjax">
      
        $η$ Pairing of Light-Emitting Fermions: Nonequilibrium Pairing Mechanism at High Temperatures
      
    </p>
    <p class="authors">
      <span class="has-text-black-bis has-text-weight-semibold">Authors:</span>
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Nakagawa%2C+M">Masaya Nakagawa</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Tsuji%2C+N">Naoto Tsuji</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Kawakami%2C+N">Norio Kawakami</a>, 
      
      <a href="/search/?searchtype=author&amp;query=Ueda%2C+M">Masahito Ueda</a>
      
